		"description": "<p><strong>Range 8 | 2 Actions | 1d12 damage</strong> <em>(Requires 1+ Mana Dice)</em></p><p>Add INT to each Mana Die rolled and deal that much extra damage to your target AND all creatures between you and it.</p><p><strong>Upgrades:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Amplified Conduit.</strong> +4 Range and +2 damage for each Mana Die.</li><li><strong>Selective Arc Filter.</strong> Damage can bypass 1 creature.</li><li><strong>Overload Dampener.</strong> –3 to repair DC. If you roll 20+ on the repair check, gain 1 action back.</li></ul><p><strong>Mishap — Arcane Overload:</strong> After the attack, suffer 2 damage per Mana Die rolled. The weapon becomes inoperable (DC 12 Finesse check to fix).</p><p><em>Selecting this invention adds the matching item to your inventory; the item itself carries the attack/defense effects and upgrades.</em></p>",
